  "text": "Moreover, 75% of TBI patients in the United States are diagnosed as suffering from mild TBI. Therefore, we used a mild/moderate 7-day TBI mouse model as described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] to investigate whether the combination (GSNO 1 CAPE) therapy shows greater efficacy compared with GSNO or CAPE alone in mitigating multimechanistic pathology of TBI.",
